# Avatar

**Figma:** [Avatar](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10526&p=f&m=dev)

Sizes, shapes, content types, and grouping below are derived from Figma node 128:10526.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Initial bg | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Initial text | `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Overflow indicator | `--bg-base-tertiary`, `--text-base-secondary` |

---

## Structure

### Content types
| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| Image | Profile photo; `rounded-full object-cover` |
| Initial | Single character only (e.g. A, B, C). Do not use multiple (e.g. AA, BB, CC)—text would overflow. |

### Initial styling
- **Background:** `--bg-brand-default`.
- **Text:** `--text-brand-on-brand`.
- **Font:** Medium or Semibold.

---

## Sizes

| Size | Dimensions |
|------|------------|
| Large | w-12 h-12 (48px) |
| Medium | w-10 h-10 (40px) – Default |
| Small | w-8 h-8 (32px) |

---

## Shapes

| Shape | Styling |
|-------|---------|
| Circle | `rounded-full` |
| Square | Radius/100–200 |

---

## Grouping

| Mode | Gap | Notes |
|------|-----|-------|
| Spaced | Space/100–200 | Between avatars |
| Overlap | Negative margin | Avatars overlap |

### Overflow indicator
- **Content:** "+N" when there are more members.
- **Style:** Smaller avatar or pill; `--bg-base-tertiary` background, `--text-base-secondary`.
- **Use:** Additional members count.

---

## With context

- Can sit next to Title + Description.
- Align with Space/200–300 gap.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10526.
